commit.message:
Minor fix (#57)

* Don't return 1 in _environ_telnet to avoid trigger the compression

and remove the redundant TELNET_TELOPT_COMPRESS2 check

Signed-off-by: Xiang Xiao <xiaoxiang@xiaomi.com>

* Fix some wrong state handler in _negotiate

Signed-off-by: Xiang Xiao <xiaoxiang@xiaomi.com>

* telet-chatd handle various corner case correctly

Signed-off-by: Xiang Xiao <xiaoxiang@xiaomi.com>

* Send "NVT"(network virtual terminal) as the default if getenv("TERM") return NULL

Signed-off-by: Xiang Xiao <xiaoxiang@xiaomi.com>

* Check POLLHUP and POLLERR in telnet poll loop

to handle the remote end close correctly

Signed-off-by: Xiang Xiao <xiaoxiang@xiaomi.com>

Minor fixes (#48)

* enable LIBTELNET_STRICT for libtelnet.c

add_compile_options only affects targets added after the command is
invoked.

* fix sign compare warnings

* fix warning when HAVE_ZLIB undefined

* allow build to complete when Doxygen is not found

* remove C++ style comment

C++ style comments are not allowed with -pedantic (unless a standard
is also specified that allows such comments).
